<H3>SimplePac</H3>
<P>
It압 possible to overdrive with the WB friendly games. This PacMan clone is build 
out of the graphic parts of the OS 2.1+. This view alone is it worth to download 
this game.
</P>
<P>
The princip of the game is well known. 
</P>
<P>
Like the ...very... interessting graphic is the funny too, some stolen samples are 
entertaining the ears. Better listen to the radio.
</P>
<P>
The Handling is simple, you can use the curser keys or a joystick via LowLevel.lib. 
Unfortunately the inquiry of the collisions in not exactly, sometimes it saves your 
life, sometimes not.
</P>
<P>
In the long run this game is not funny.
</P>
<P>
An interessting feature: You can scale the game field freely. My commputer resets 
sometimes if I try this.
</P>
<P>
Sum: It is a good game for a play at times but boring in the long run.
</P>
