<H3>Lord of Alcandria 3</H3>
<P>
This game is the last one because it is an adventure and I have not enough time to 
play it. This is way I just introduce it without any rating.
</P>
<P>
Lord of Alcandria is a Point&amp;Click Adventure in the well known style like
Maniac Mansion, Loom or Monkey Island.
This is the story of the game:
</P>
<P>
You are Krilok Rainwood, who gets to the County of Lotharia by accident. This 
county ruled Lord Hellock. His brother Krislow ruled the next-door county 
Alcandria. Hellock wanted to possess both and in a battle for this he died.
Short after this the brother died, too.
</P>
<P>
The new Lord of Letharia is a bad man and is dominated by Hellok out of another 
dimension. Many children have been kidnapped.
</P>
<P>
Before the first mouse click you can already see that the graphic and the sound is 
excellent. The qualitiy is like the one of Monkey Island3 or Simon the Sorcerer, 
thein-game graphic as well as the animation in the beginning
</P>
<P>
As mentioned above, I haven앖 played the game as much and so I do not want to 
tell any false.
</P>
<P>
No rating today.
</P>
